snippet.title: Human Error - Traitor Mode Intro
snippet.description: Human Error Coop comes with the Traitor Mode where one of the four players is selected as a Traitor in the beginning of each round. You can read more and download here: http://hlssmod.net/index.php?page=0&news=13
